This app was created by incredibly talented artists and executed exceptionally well by creative and technical developers alike who deserve the financial backing to keep improving the app and creating new ones. As an photo editing app, Photo Lab is great fun and produces enjoyable and eye-catching images.  I would have given Photo Lab Pro five stars, but it suffers from two problems, one of which is severe, and the other an annoyance.  Photo Lab Pro can only work with photos that are already on your phone. Photos that you've stored in the cloud, on Google Photos or Dropbox for instance, are out of Photo Lab's reach -- a big drawback.  As for the annoyance, Photo Lab ads the text, "Created with Photo Lab app #photolab" when you share photos. It would be nice for paid users to be able to turn that self-promotion off.
